## Runtime architecture

**Single source of truth:** PostgreSQL.

**Desktop Edition**

```
Electron â†’ React â†’ apiClient (/api/v1) â†’ Express API â†’ modules (routesâ†’servicesâ†’repositories) â†’ FinancialPostingService â†’ PostgreSQL
```

**Cloud Edition**

```
Browser â†’ React â†’ apiClient (/api/v1) â†’ Express API â†’ modules (routesâ†’servicesâ†’repositories) â†’ FinancialPostingService â†’ PostgreSQL
```

**Shared packages:** `shared/financial-core/`, `shared/report-engines/`, `shared/rbac/`

